To run openttd you need data files provided by the original Transport
Tycoon Deluxe.

The following files should be copied to ${PREFIX}/share/games/openttd/data
in order to play:

	sample.cat
	trg1r.grf
	trgcr.grf
	trghr.grf
	trgir.grf
	trgtr.grf

===========================================================================
